# Description:
#    This primitive obtains the Michelle saturation level in ADU for the current
#    frame.
#
#    The saturation level is returned through an argument.
#
# Arguments:
#    SATURATION = REAL (Returned)
#       The saturation level obtained.
#
# Notes:
#    -  This primitive is only suitable for Michelle.
#    -  It merely uses an approximnate constant.  At present the level is
#    not well determined.
